{"tid":1921740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國公布2019年人權報告 痛批中國是「世紀汙點」","createTime":"2020-03-12T06:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T07:11:23.000Z","uid":28765,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"01a30c52f862a3df7efc07883a33358a37fe2a7b","tid":1921740,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"2020-03-12 10:49:29<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國國務院今日發布2019年度各國別人權報告，直接點名中國對新疆維族人以至對全國人民的集體迫害行為是「世紀汙點」（stain of the century）。<br />\n<br />\n根據《美國之音》報導，美國國務卿龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）於美東時間11日在人權報告發表會上演說，重點強調中國、伊朗、委內瑞拉及古巴等4個國家在2019年具有低劣的人權紀錄，其中尤以中國為重。<br />\n<br />\n報告提到，中國政府在過去一年持續進行非法殺害、強迫失蹤、酷刑、任意拘留，對記者、律師、作家、異議者、上訪者及其家人的人身攻擊與刑事起訴，以及言論審查與強制性生育等政策。<br />\n<br />\n龐皮歐更重點提及中國對新疆的高壓政策，稱當局在新疆強制關押逾百萬少數民族穆斯林，實施再教育運動，他說，「當局將信教的少數族群集體囚禁於集中營中，如我過去所說，中國在新疆的劣跡就是世紀汙點」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3097049\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3097049&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=15c7a639\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3097049&h=bb3f925d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3097049</a>"},{"pid":"0c15bd21f78890e9d1d401e5d6030d91fa870d11","tid":1921740,"uid":218855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:58:15.000Z","msg":"美軍來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8187792bf1eb56b1610f0100a46be97a2869e463","tid":1921740,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8731fe40dc9b5e193e937ffb018e96c309b66671","tid":1921740,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"汙點国又有新名<im